                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word God is not rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works</desc>
                  <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#116v #117r" facs="121">folss. 116v, 117r, </locus> (Ps. 150), <locus target="#125v #126r #126v" facs="130 131">125v, 126r, 126v</locus> (tenth biblical canticle)</desc>
