                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#149r" facs="153">Fol. 149r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref> with caption <q>“Saint Mika’el,” “Icon of Our Lady Mary,” “Saint Gabri’el.”</q></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#1r #41r #80r #117v #129v #136r #144v" facs="005 045 084 122 134 140 149">folss. 1r, 41r, 80r, 117v, 129v, 136r, 144v, </locus> (colorful ornate haräg);
                    <locus target="#7v #15v #24r #33v #40v #46v #55r #65v #73v #92r #102v #105v #111v #117v" facs="012 020 028 038 045 051 059 070 078 096 107 110 116 122">7v, 15v, 24r, 33v, 40v, 46v, 55r, 65v, 73v, 92r, 102v, 105v, 111v, 117v, </locus> (line of alternating red and black dots);
                    <locus target="#79r #135v #148v" facs="083 140 153">79r, 135v, 148v</locus> (full stops between lines of red and black dots)
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
